description: A scalable microservice-based E-commerce web application for a fake film festival. Deployed on a Kubernetes Cluster using Docker. Includes technologies: Typescript, Express, Next.js, SasS, Jest, Digital Ocean, Google Cloud Platform (GCP), RESTful API, Skaffold, Ingress-Nginx, NATS Streaming Service, CI/CD, and MongoDB.
